Intimation of Board Meeting under Regulation 29(1)(d) and 50(1)(d) of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015

Please be informed that a Meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled to be held on Tuesday, October 22, 2024, to, inter alia, consider approval of the audited standalone and consolidated financial statements and financial results of the Company for the quarter and half year ended September 30, 2024.

Please be informed that a Meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled to be held on Tuesday, July 23, 2024, to, inter alia, consider approval of the audited standalone and consolidated financial statements and financial results of the Company for the quarter ended June 30, 2024.
